{"tid":1543740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷搭黨鐵] 一蚊都唔俾呀屌你","createTime":"2019-09-05T09:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:31:43.000Z","uid":237226,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"180935b6d528d89c69b4bb86eab79ff6c3e1c3a1","tid":1543740,"uid":237226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"屌你班仆街咁撚得閒去做查飛狗捉人跳閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我港島出九龍返學再去新界做野一程鐵都唔搭呀<br />\n<br />\n有廢老卡都唔用 1.9都唔俾你賺呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民罷搭黨鐵呀 唔好唔記得佢地點樣做幫凶對付我地既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6973f8641eeb3ab615b55080af5f95f36eed251d","tid":1543740,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf23870cdbc58dd3be8ecfee1f2b022babe42342","tid":1543740,"uid":237226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"交Cctv呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d3716ae9cf9165c9006566b550a2dd9fd545f5","tid":1543740,"uid":237226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"聽晚1930遮打花園"},{"pid":"fef0991a1dee113a69c6eaeb5b0770030178848d","tid":1543740,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n9人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8udugLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8udugLx.jpg&h=bae3ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=b1611477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"f4c0426d404eafd477de247532c9cc34c9f42372","tid":1543740,"uid":237226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"9月8 1400美國駐港澳總領事館"},{"pid":"a6bd38be05500e845ea6a6f28b3893cb373ffd3f","